SEC. 2. Section thirty-eight-A is hereby amended to read as follows:

"SEC. 38-A.

Organization of the Office into three divisions.

âTo promote a more efficient performance of the functions and duties of the office, the City Fiscal shall organized said office into three divisions as follows:

"(

a

) Preliminary Investigation Division which shall have exclusive charge of the conduct, of preliminary investigations of all crimes and violations of city ordinances;

"(

b

) Prosecution Division which shall have exclusive charge of the prosecution of criminal cases; and

"(

c

) Miscellaneous Division which shall represent the city in all civil cases wherein the city or any officer thereof , in his official capacity is a party, render opinions, draw ordinances when required by the Board, contracts, bonds, and inspect and pass upon all such documents already drawn but pending approval by the city officer concerned.
